#### 序列化类Serilizer.py

```python
from django.core import serializers  # django自带的序列化
from django.forms.models import model_to_dict  # 查询集直接转化为字典

from rest_framework.serializers import Serializer  # 简单model的序列化，没有外键
from rest_framework.serializers import ModelSerializer  # 外键model序列化
```

